oai_dc:dc.dc:title: West End Avenue at Seventeenth, Nashville, Tennessee, circa 1951 April 02
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A view of West End Avenue at Seventeenth, circa April 2nd, 1951. A large commercial truck had overturned onto its side near the site. Commercial businesses that are pictured include Robertson Tire Company, Buntley-Sanders Motors, Gower Floor Covering (1704 West End Avenue), and Kroger (1705 West End Avenue). Forms part of Record Group 3, Metro Davidson County Photographer. 1 photograph negative : b & w ; 4 x 5 in.
